  "title": "Smoked Fish - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "Smoked Fish is an Artisan Good made from the Fish Smoker using any fish and 1 coal, taking 50 minutes. It doubles the sell price of the fish while retaining quality, as well as multiplying the energy and health restoration by 1.5 (if that fish restored energy or health, otherwise the value remains unchanged).[1] The smoker accepts Legendary Fish as well as Crab Pot specific fish, making the latter edible.[2]",
